** New Trader to MyArtisanMarkets**
Introducing Whispers of Wood! John makes these beautiful boards at home and they are both stiking and functional. 
___

How often are you stuck without a nice board to present your bread/cheese on at a get together? We think about what food we are serving, but if you are like me, don’t think how it is to be displayed. Well visit Whispers of Wood at a market near you soon and get sorted before your next event.

In case you missed last Sunday, we talked more in depth about serving the world around us by loving people. Whether we care for them or not, we can be a game changer by showing them Jesus through our actions. A tangible way we are going to do that is by serving in Broadway Kids. We are serving in kids ministry BOTH hours on Sunday, May 28th! Cam & Tulla will put together which students serve where during first & second hour, so be on the lookout for that info. I hope everyone out there who is feeling a certain way allows themselves time to grow and develop into the wonderful person they are destined to be. Live your life for you and no one else! The dark clouds that sit up inside your mind and heart will soon disappear, give yourself a chance.... don't be too hard on yourself, and the most important thing of all!
